<li>"The Fake Crisis"<sup id="cite_ref-www.rollingstone.com.669_137-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-www.rollingstone.com.669-137" title=""><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup>- <i><a href="/wiki/Rolling_Stone" title="Rolling Stone">Rolling Stone</a></i></li>
<li>"What Does Price Indexing Mean for Social Security Benefits?"<sup id="cite_ref-www.bc.edu.670_138-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-www.bc.edu.670-138" title=""><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup>- from Center for Retirement Research, January, 2005 (explanation of wage indexing versus price indexing)</li>
